<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Cart Reminder - Bamboo Shop</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f6f9fc;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #2b7a0b;
    }
    p {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    a.button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: #2b7a0b;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    a.button:hover {
      background: #25660a;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>You left some items in your cart! Don't miss out-complete your purchase before they are gone.</p>

    <ul>
      {{#each cart.items}}
        <li>
          <strong>{{this.product.name}}</strong> - Quantity: {{this.quantity}}
        </li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <p>Hurry! Complete your order before your items go out of stock.</p>

    <p>
      <a class="button" href="{{appUrl}}/cart" target="_blank">Go to Cart</a>
    </p>

    <p>Thank you for shopping with Bamboo Shop!</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br/>Bamboo Shop Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
